commentAnnotations.text: Participants will use Mode 1 only for all sessions of the face mask - the neck and chest mask does not have multiple settings
The lower straps are optional and are designed to allow the user to pull the mask closer to the face
commentAnnotations.sourceSection: Directions For Use - Face Mask Set Up

commentAnnotations.text: If the (Start/Pause) button is not pressed within 30 seconds once a mode is selected, the mask will turn off automatically
commentAnnotations.sourceSection: Directions For Use - Face Mask Step 2

commentAnnotations.text: If the (Start/Pause) button is not pressed within 30 seconds during a paused session, the mask will turn off automatically
commentAnnotations.sourceSection: Directions For Use - Face Mask Step 3

commentAnnotations.text: If you don't press the (Start/Pause) button within 30 seconds, the mask will shut off automatically
commentAnnotations.sourceSection: Directions For Use - Neck & Chest Mask Step 2
